trans-unit.source: Provides an editor that can perform default file searching for bitmap (.bmp) files.
trans-unit.target: Gir et redigeringsprogram som kan utføre standardfil søker for punktgrafikkfiler (*.bmp).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.ImageListImageEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Design.ImageListImageEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Edits the specified object value using the edit style provided by the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ImageEditor.GetEditStyle*> method.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer det angitte objektverdien Rediger stilen fra den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ImageEditor.GetEditStyle*>metoden.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ImageEditor.GetEditStyle*>

trans-unit.source: This editor uses a service provider to obtain any necessary editing services.
trans-unit.target: Dette redigeringsprogrammet bruker en leverandør for å hente noen nødvendige redigering tjenester.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.IServiceProvider> through which editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.IServiceProvider>som redigering services kan hentes.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> being edited.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>redigeres.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: An <xref:System.Object> representing the new value.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Object>som representerer den nye verdien.</xref:System.Object>

trans-unit.source: If the value of the object has not changed, the EditValue method returns the object that was passed to it.
trans-unit.target: Hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, returnerer metoden EditValue objektet som ble sendt til den.

trans-unit.source: Gets the description for the default file-list filter provided by this editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter beskrivelsen for listen over filer Standardfiltret av dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The file dialog box description appears in the file-list filter drop-down list box.
trans-unit.target: Filen dialogboksen for beskrivelse vises i listen over filer rullegardinlisten filterboksen.

trans-unit.source: The description for the default file-list filter.
trans-unit.target: Beskrivelsen standard filliste filteret.

trans-unit.source: Gets an array of supported image types.
trans-unit.target: Henter en matrise av støttede bildetyper.

trans-unit.source: An array of <xref:System.Type> representing supported image types.
trans-unit.target: En matrise av <xref:System.Type>som representerer støttede bildetyper.</xref:System.Type>

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether this editor supports painting a representation of an object's value.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om dette redigeringsprogrammet støtter maler en representasjon av verdien for et objekt.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> that can be used to gain additional context information.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> som kan brukes til å få ytterligere kontekstinformasjon.

trans-unit.source: Paints a value indicated by the specified <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Maler en verdi som er angitt av den angitte <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: To display the representation of the value in the typical property sheet format, paint within the boundaries of the <xref:System.Drawing.Rectangle> contained within the specified <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil vise representasjon av verdien formatet vanlige egenskapen arket, fargemerknader i grensene for <xref:System.Drawing.Rectangle>innenfor det angitte <xref:System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs>.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs> </xref:System.Drawing.Rectangle>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs"></xref> indicating what to paint and where to paint it.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Drawing.Design.PaintValueEventArgs"> </xref> som viser hva du maler og hvor du fargemerknader i den.
